ALIW AWARDS 2022

December 5, 2022, 6:00PM
@FIESTA PAVILLION, MANILA HOTEL



Our very own PANDANGO SA ILAW PERFORMERS will exhibit our very own original folk dance " Pandango sa Ilaw" in the cultural presentation, beaming with pride and versatility in folkloric dance competition.
The 35th Annual Aliw Awards presentation on Aliw Awards Foundation’s 45th year will take place on December 5,2022 at the prestigious Manila Hotel’s Fiesta Pavilion, after an absence of a year, due to the Covid-19 pandemic.



AWARDS:
MUNICIPALITY OF LUBANG

"BEST FESTIVAL PRACTICES AND PERFORMANCE"
(PANDANGO SA ILAW)
"BEST FESTIVAL CATALYST/ORGANIZER
(Hon. MAYOR MICHAEL LIM ORAYANI)
